Dr. Bornovali is also coordinating the restoration and renovation of the Istanbul Italian Society’s Garibaldi House (Società Operaia Italiana di Mutuo Soccorso) in [[Beyoğlu]].<ref>{{Citation| last =| first = | title = Garibaldi House, A New Cultural Temple in Istanbul| journal = TÜRSAB Magazine| volume =| date = March 2014| issue = 345| pages = 18–24| url = http://www.tursab.org.tr/yayin/103/mart_2014_103_6349665.pdf}}</ref>
